headline.print_headline: Rossouw Gets South Africa Test Call-Up
headline.main: Rossouw Gets South Africa Test Call-Up

lead_paragraph: South Africa have called left-handed batsman Rilee Rossouw into their squad for the remaining two tests against West Indies after wicketkeeper Quinton de Kock was ruled out through injury.
